intended for investments
in our youth startups.

24
00:01:35,678 --> 00:01:36,763
Is that correct?

25
00:01:36,846 --> 00:01:39,182
Yes, that's right.

26
00:01:41,017 --> 00:01:42,018
Sir,

27
