got their sources.

46
00:02:51,004 --> 00:02:52,755
It was from the prosecution.

47
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:57,135
Seokhwan, we're alumni.
What year did you graduate?

48
00:02:59,179 --> 00:03:00,555
-Excuse me?
-[Myeongja laughs]

49
00:03:01,222 --> 00:03:02,223
