100
00:06:19,212 --> 00:06:20,380
I, Ahn Myeongja,

101
00:06:20,463 --> 00:06:22,590
will overcome this, not for my future...

102
00:06:22,673 --> 00:06:23,674
EP04. EXIT STRATEGY

103
00:06:23,758 --> 00:06:25,676
