of your kind to come along?

223
00:12:20,364 --> 00:12:21,407
[Myeongja chuckles]

224
00:12:22,450 --> 00:12:25,995
Still, we survived.

225
00:12:27,079 --> 00:12:28,956
We begged in the dirt,

226
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:31,500
