234
00:12:57,860 --> 00:12:58,861
Yes, sir.

235
00:12:59,361 --> 00:13:01,071
Thank you for your answer.

236
00:13:14,627 --> 00:13:16,796
-[scoffs]
-[door closes]

237
00:13:17,713 --> 00:13:20,341
