at this rate?

251
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:58,045
Exactly. The party could
help a little at a time like this.

252
00:13:58,420 --> 00:13:59,421
[Myeongja laughs]

253
00:14:03,342 --> 00:14:04,343
Ah.

254
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:06,262
