for her trip to Spain.

587
00:30:26,616 --> 00:30:28,618
-[Myeongja sniffs]
-[camera shutters clicking]

588
00:30:30,286 --> 00:30:31,496
Last night,

589
00:30:32,956 --> 00:30:36,209
